gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"India"}],["$","span","custom software development",{"className":"text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"custom software development"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-goated","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Finding the right software agency in India can make or break your project. India has become a global hub for software development, but with thousands of agencies to choose from, identifying the ones that actually deliver is the real challenge."}]]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"We put together this list based on three criteria: the quality of their shipped work, their ability to deliver on time, and real client outcomes. No paid placements. No affiliate links."}]]}],["$","h2","2",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"1. GOATED. (Mumbai)"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Custom software development and AI automation"}]]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"GOATED. is a Mumbai-based agency that builds bespoke software and AI automation systems from scratch. They work across healthcare, music, e-commerce, and creative industries. Their approach is distinctive: no templates, no off-the-shelf components, and working prototypes delivered within two weeks."}]]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Notable projects include a catalogue management system for Azadi Records, a booking automation platform for a physiotherapy clinic in South Bombay, and the full e-commerce infrastructure for Wear World Peace (founded by NBA player Ron Artest)."}]]}],["$","p","6",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Businesses that need fully custom solutions with fast turnaround."}]]}],["$","h2","7",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"2. Thoughtworks (Bangalore, Pune, Chennai)"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Enterprise software consulting and agile transformation"}]]}],["$","p","9",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Thoughtworks is one of the most respected names in global software consulting. They pioneered many of the agile and continuous delivery practices that are now industry standard. Their India offices handle some of the most complex enterprise transformations in the country."}]]}],["$","p","10",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Large enterprises undergoing digital transformation."}]]}],["$","h2","11",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"3. Hasura (Bangalore)"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" API development and data infrastructure"}]]}],["$","p","13",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Hasura built one of the most popular open-source GraphQL engines in the world, and their consulting arm helps companies build high-performance API layers. Their India team is deeply technical and focused on developer experience."}]]}],["$","p","14",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Companies that need robust API and data infrastructure."}]]}],["$","h2","15",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"4. Tarkalabs (Pune)"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Product engineering and design"}]]}],["$","p","17",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Tarkalabs focuses on building digital products from concept to launch. They combine strong design thinking with solid engineering, making them a good choice for startups and mid-size companies building consumer-facing products."}]]}],["$","p","18",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Product companies that need end-to-end design and engineering."}]]}],["$","h2","19",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"5. Setu (Bangalore)"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Fintech infrastructure and API platforms"}]]}],["$","p","21",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Setu specialises in building financial infrastructure. They have built APIs that power payments, account aggregation, and lending workflows for some of India's largest fintech companies. Their engineering quality is exceptionally high."}]]}],["$","p","22",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Fintech companies and businesses integrating financial services."}]]}],["$","h2","23",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"6. Nilenso (Bangalore)"}],["$","p","24",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Functional programming and backend systems"}]]}],["$","p","25",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Nilenso is a worker-owned cooperative that builds complex backend systems using Clojure, Haskell, and other functional programming languages. They are the team you call when your system needs to be bulletproof."}]]}],["$","p","26",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Companies with complex data processing or distributed systems needs."}]]}],["$","h2","27",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"7. Obvious (Bangalore)"}],["$","p","28",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Mobile and product design"}]]}],["$","p","29",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Obvious builds mobile applications and digital products with a strong emphasis on design. They have worked with some of India's most well-known startups and are particularly strong in the healthcare and fintech space."}]]}],["$","p","30",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Mobile-first products that need excellent UX."}]]}],["$","h2","31",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"8. Commutatus (Mumbai)"}],["$","p","32",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Web and mobile development for startups"}]]}],["$","p","33",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Commutatus is a Mumbai-based agency that works primarily with early-stage startups. They move fast, keep teams small, and focus on shipping MVPs that can scale."}]]}],["$","p","34",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Startups that need to move from idea to MVP quickly."}]]}],["$","h2","35",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"9. GeekyAnts (Bangalore)"}],["$","p","36",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" React Native and cross-platform development"}]]}],["$","p","37",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"GeekyAnts is one of India's most prominent React Native development shops. They have contributed to the open-source ecosystem significantly and build cross-platform mobile apps for companies worldwide."}]]}],["$","p","38",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Companies that need cross-platform mobile applications."}]]}],["$","h2","39",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"10. Frappe (Mumbai)"}],["$","p","40",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Speciality:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Open-source ERP and business tools"}]]}],["$","p","41",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Frappe builds ERPNext, one of the most popular open-source ERP systems in the world. Their team also does custom development on top of the Frappe framework, making them ideal for businesses that want open-source-first solutions."}]]}],["$","p","42",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Best for:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Businesses looking for open-source ERP and business management tools."}]]}],["$","h2","43",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"How to choose the right software agency"}],["$","p","44",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"The best agency for your project depends on what you are building, how fast you need it, and how custom the solution needs to be. Here are some questions to ask:"}]]}],["$","li","45",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Do they show real shipped work?"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Case studies with measurable outcomes matter more than client logos."}]]}],["$","li","46",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"How fast do they deliver?"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" Agencies that take months to deliver a prototype are often over-engineering or under-staffed."}]]}],["$","li","47",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Do they build custom or use templates?"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" If your business has unique workflows, template-based solutions will create more problems than they solve."}]]}],["$","li","48",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"What happens after launch?"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" The best agencies document everything and hand over clean, so you are not locked into a retainer."}]]}],["$","li","49",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 m